<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201115/4dedaf3e7ac94c719299cbb273695dd5.png" /></p>
<p><strong><span><span>北京消费者</span><span>周金洋</span></span><span><span>：</span></span></strong><span><span>更喜欢国货产品</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>特别经济，用起来比较舒服。</span></span></p>
